text: Cynthia Onyedikachi Aku (born December 31, 1999) is a Nigerian professional footballer, who plays for Rivers Angels in the Nigeria Women Premier League. Aku represented Nigeria at youth level, before making her debut for the senior team. At the 2019 WAFU Zone B Women's Cup, she was named player of the match in Nigeria's 15-0 victory against Niger. ==References== == External links == * Category:Nigerian women's footballers Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Rivers Angels F.C. players
